
Version 0.2.1
===========
    + Properly detect HTTP client disconnects - prevent
    resource leakage under certain conditions

    + Fixed bug which made first few seconds of HTTP stream
    unplayable

Version 0.2
===========
    * Added HTTP "continuous download" streaming

    + Added support for RTP UDP multicast sources

    + Improved support of multiple clients with same
    IP address via RTSP

    + Set IP TOS and socket priority for RTP streams


Version 0.1
===========
    Initial release.
